{"tid":2423650,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Paramount推出串流電視 《職業特工隊7》上畫個半月即上串流","createTime":"2021-02-26T04:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T04:36:56.000Z","uid":117117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e54b7dcc0e5f967e13df7cc90853327612f9703a","tid":2423650,"uid":117117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"近來串流電視大行其道，間間電影公司都轉為發展串流，最近ViacomCBS就宣佈，旗下電影公司Paramount將於下月4號推出串流電視Paramount Plus，更以兩部大作《職業特工隊7》（Mission: Impossible 7）與《無聲絕境2》（A Quiet Place Part II）打頭炮，戲院上畫個半月即上串流有得睇。<br />\n<br />\n華納兄弟將電影與串流同步推出被鬧爆，Paramount有見及此，就打算將大作照上戲院搵真銀，再將作品極速放上串流電視吸家庭客。《職業特工隊7》原定於今年11月19日上映，而《無聲絕境2》就於9月17日上映，現時兩部作品都會在上畫45日後放上串流電視。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dPGfo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dPGfo3.png&h=22143bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210226/PF7LEB6TFBETLAFILQINGRILGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210226%2FPF7LEB6TFBETLAFILQINGRILGI%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=123f3208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210226%2FPF7LEB6TFBETLAFILQINGRILGI%2F&h=4a5f3286\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210226/PF7LEB6TFBETLAFILQINGRILGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲比top gun 2我睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3858632e20d4981db105d4f53441acedb4da27b0","tid":2423650,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"個個都搞ott"},{"pid":"b95005496b10886a84109703489137d0296475e8","tid":2423650,"uid":117117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3858632e20d4981db105d4f53441acedb4da27b0","tid":2423650,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"個個都搞ott"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20